3. cs.RO (Robotics) - TSP is a well-known problem in robotics, and the paper discusses the performance of different algorithms in solving it. 
4. cs.CC (Computational Complexity) - The paper discusses the difficulty of TSP and HCP instances and how different algorithms perform on them, which is related to computational complexity. 
5. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper mentions the use of heuristics and optimization techniques, which are commonly used in neural and evolutionary computing.
